# Refine UI Contrast and Swipe Behavior

## Goal
1.  **Swipe to Save**: Ensure the slider stays in the "saved" position after completion, without resetting automatically.
2.  **UI Contrast**: Increase visual distinction between the top app bar, the middle content area, and the bottom navigation bar.

## Proposed Changes

### [lib/widgets/swipe_to_save_widget.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/widgets/swipe_to_save_widget.dart)
- [MODIFY] In [_completeSwipe](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/widgets/swipe_to_save_widget.dart#66-84), remove the `Future.delayed` block that resets `_isCompleted` and `_dragValue`.

